<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.7">
<l>kaṭṭēṟu nīḷcōlaik kāṇṭavattait tīmūṭṭi</l>
<l>viṭṭāṉai meyya mamarnta perumāṉai</l>
<l>maṭṭēṟu kaṟpakattai mātarkkāy vaṇtuvarai</l>
<l>naṭṭāṉai nāṭi naṟaiyūril kaṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having searched for the one who set fire and kindled</l>
<l>The vast Khāṇḍava forest where guards were many,</l>
<l>The great lord who dwells in Meyyam, the one who planted</l>
<l>The kalpaka tree, where nectar swells, in prosperous Dwārakā for his lady,</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw [him] in Naṟaiyūr</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
